{"tid":773045,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳馬斯克搵軟銀幫手私有化Tesla","createTime":"2018-08-09T08:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T12:06:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25047bd6b1cd3b9f9646807981ff11ec412330b7","tid":773045,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"Tesla行政總裁馬斯克Elon Musk日前確認有意私有化Tesla，根據外電報道引述消息人土指，Elon Musk去年已跟日本軟銀的孫正義商討將Tesla私有化的可能性，包括軟銀入股Tesla。Tesla股價日前升11%，昨晚轉跌2.4%，市後報369.5美元。<br />\n<br />\n華爾街當地認為，Elon Musk沒有足夠資金將Tesla私有化，若以他提出每股420美元私有化，涉及資金高達720億美元。<br />\n另外，美國證交會SEC亦已去信Elon Musk，向其查問在社交媒體公布私有化的動機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180809/large/1533775950_0a21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180809%2Flarge%2F1533775950_0a21.jpg&h=7271d0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180809/58540752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F58540752&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=e85223a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F58540752&h=e1954a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180809/58540752</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又係孫正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fca0d5d6452d7e69c24de68fb928bfbe37acb14","tid":773045,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T08:28:23.000Z","msg":"人地緊係搵到水喉先出聲"},{"pid":"b9320339ff17861b735007a50099c210f30e9242","tid":773045,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"做市，拉得。"}]}